{"tid":621372,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人留意今年嘅潑水節？","createTime":"2018-04-08T09:16:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-09T05:35:14.000Z","uid":101935,"like":23,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a63540a2648615ff16108b7256a40c1134da7699","tid":621372,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:16:18.000Z","msg":"印象中每年香港都會喺九龍城搞個潑水節，封幾條街然後啲人就拎住水槍周圍射下巡遊下，之前幾年都有去，的確幾好氣氛。<br />\n<br />\n直到今年四月頭，開始見到九龍城出現呢啲宣傳，ig，yahoo周圍都睇到。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/171539_9d164e49dafdf77272f005bc6ed24c54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F171539_9d164e49dafdf77272f005bc6ed24c54.png&h=a36a68c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當刻覺得有啲商業化，心諗咁奇怪泰國野唔去九龍城但去荔枝角？但最後今日都去睇下係點啦，對佢都仲有少少期望。<br />\n<br />\n一出D2，聽到音樂都好似幾有氣氛，諗住都ok啦應該。<br />\n<br />\n點知，嘩屌。<br />\n劃咗個乜撚野「激戰區」，啲人就喺入面射下水，完全無咗九龍城有得周街走跑來跑去射人嗰種感覺，圍住個框大家射下水，我點解唔去沙灘？得個框咁比我，而家敷衍定施捨？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/08/171600_b91745437ebe522165aa308bee7ec82d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F08%2F171600_b91745437ebe522165aa308bee7ec82d.png&h=17347b7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好啦唔緊要，即管就去睇下佢個泰國市集有幾把炮。上到去個乜鳩d2 place，再屌多聲。完全係拎左個潑水節嚟比商家佬發個財。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n一個叫做有特式少少既活動都搞到咁，成個活動最特別係可以喺條街射下水，而家是鳩但劃個框比你滿足下你就將大半個重點放去市集賺你錢，香港真係無撚得救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱開錯台 我唔信無人留意<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/01.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c972b1f3c48370abdc9c1f4cd66dd82745c9e510","tid":621372,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0352d3837b835517f6f39c771f54c7217132b107","tid":621372,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:16:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ced4d04dcd966b8bf019e4527932ceccb0d5711","tid":621372,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e35786e49caea640db829bdb05c0d127515326","tid":621372,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"搞得好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16e6ca2fc13bd337461f7b18f4663fed3f4461a3","tid":621372,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4ced4d04dcd966b8bf019e4527932ceccb0d5711","tid":621372,"uid":94828,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:17:36.000Z","msg":"真係冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:19:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bf26d159d18921e9dd7ef65e1c8b27acceddca0","tid":621372,"uid":101935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"88e35786e49caea640db829bdb05c0d127515326","tid":621372,"uid":56439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:19:23.000Z","msg":"搞得好撚柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T09:20:32.000Z","msg":"你都有去？真係屌屌聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class